title: Video Spotlight: Central Dauphin RB Raleigh Sirb
text: Video Spotlight: Central Dauphin RB Raleigh Sirb Ed O'Brien PaPreps.com Publisher PA PREPS was on hand for the Harrisburg/Central Dauphin game this past Friday night and one of the standout players was Central Dauphin running back Raleigh Sirb. Sirb carried the ball 17 times for 137 yards and four touchdowns in a little less than three quarters of play. Sirb is averaging 100.8 yards per game so far through four contests and has scored ten total touchdowns. Below is video footage of his performance.
